Hi Emiliano,
you can't make an activity without modifying the code... We are planningto make sugar more compatible with traditional applications (latest gitis a bit better at this already) but that's a different matter.
I'm curious about the reason you are trying to add a file manager toSugar. "File management" will be handled by the journal:
http://wiki.laptop.org/go/OLPC_Human_Interface_Guidelines/The_Laptop_Experience/The_Journal
